FFlagStudioFixStandalonePluginUnloadingA.mechanism: Improves how Studio handles plugin unloading.
FFlagStudioFixStandalonePluginUnloadingA.purpose: Makes Studio more stable and less prone to crashing, especially when using many plugins.

DFIntLoadTestParticipationPerMillionUser.mechanism: Controls the percentage of users included in load tests for a specific filter.
DFIntLoadTestParticipationPerMillionUser.purpose: Allows Roblox to test new features on a subset of players to identify and fix issues before a wider release.  The filter specifies which places are included in the test.

DFIntTextChatCommandClientSentThrottlePe.mechanism: Limits how often players can send text chat commands.
DFIntTextChatCommandClientSentThrottlePe.purpose: Reduces spam and potential abuse of in-game chat commands.

FFlagIsrMainMetrics_Staged.mechanism: Enables collection of key performance metrics.
FFlagIsrMainMetrics_Staged.purpose: Helps Roblox identify and improve performance bottlenecks in the game, leading to a smoother experience for players.

DFFlagSkipSavingEmptyCapture.mechanism: Prevents saving capture data if it's empty.
DFFlagSkipSavingEmptyCapture.purpose: Improves efficiency by reducing unnecessary storage usage and saving time.

FFlagVideoGamePreviewSessionTracking.mechanism: Tracks player activity during video game previews.
FFlagVideoGamePreviewSessionTracking.purpose: Helps Roblox understand player engagement with previews, informing game development and marketing decisions.

FFlagEnableProfilePlatformDualCta_v5.mechanism: Displays two calls-to-action (CTAs) on user profiles.
FFlagEnableProfilePlatformDualCta_v5.purpose: May improve user experience by giving users more options related to their profiles (e.g., following and messaging).  Version 5 implies an iteration on prior versions.

FFlagVoiceAddWebrtClosedTransitionEnable.mechanism: Improves the transition when ending a WebRTC voice chat session.
FFlagVoiceAddWebrtClosedTransitionEnable.purpose: Provides a smoother and more reliable voice chat experience, reducing disruptions and improving audio quality.

FFlagEnableCVSUrlForOtaPatch_Staged.mechanism: This flag allows Roblox to use a specific URL for delivering updates to players' games.
FFlagEnableCVSUrlForOtaPatch_Staged.purpose: It helps ensure that players receive the latest game patches more efficiently.

DFFlagSkipSavingEmptyCapture_Staged.mechanism: This flag prevents the system from saving data when there is nothing to save.
DFFlagSkipSavingEmptyCapture_Staged.purpose: It improves performance by reducing unnecessary data storage and processing.

DFIntJoinLimitWin32x64.mechanism: This flag sets a limit on the number of players who can join a game on 64-bit Windows systems.
DFIntJoinLimitWin32x64.purpose: It helps maintain game stability by preventing overcrowding on servers.

FFlagReconnectToSameServer.mechanism: Client attempts to reconnect to the same game server after a disconnect.
FFlagReconnectToSameServer.purpose: Reduces the chance of players joining a different server after a temporary interruption, keeping them with their friends and progress.

FFlagNetworkInterface.mechanism: Allows Roblox to select the best network interface for communication.
FFlagNetworkInterface.purpose: Improves connection stability and speed by choosing the optimal network adapter (e.g., wired over Wi-Fi).

FFlagVoiceAddWebrtClosedTransitionEnable.mechanism: Improves the handling of voice chat connections using WebRTC.
FFlagVoiceAddWebrtClosedTransitionEnable.purpose: Reduces audio glitches and improves the reliability of voice chat.

DFIntRobloxTelemetryLoadTestStartThrottl.mechanism: Controls the percentage of users included in load tests for place filters.
DFIntRobloxTelemetryLoadTestStartThrottl.purpose: Allows controlled testing of new features related to searching and filtering places without impacting all users.

FFlagNetworkInterface_Staged.mechanism: This flag enables a new way for Roblox to handle network connections, improving how data is sent and received.
FFlagNetworkInterface_Staged.purpose: It aims to make the game experience smoother and reduce lag for players.

DFIntProductIdProductInfoCacheLifetimeSe.mechanism: This flag controls how long product information is stored before it needs to be refreshed.
DFIntProductIdProductInfoCacheLifetimeSe.purpose: It helps speed up access to product details, making it quicker for players to see and buy items.
